Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:44.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那她什么时候回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:48.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我看看…但需绕行一处
