Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:54.51,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}双手便不由自主   伸向旧日光景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.78,0:02:01.11,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}但孤身一人    也许有些话语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:04.62,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}难以领悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:09.21,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}一句「再见」伤感不已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:16.27,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}一声「爱你」遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:24.36,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}这份思念无法言喻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:31.68,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}让人惶恐    却又无比令人怜惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:37.94,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}我眼中的泪 到底为何而流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:44.67,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}纠缠不清的心 到底如何回应
