Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:57.66,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}埋藏在心里    一句又一句
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:03:06.50,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}我止不住地想见到你
